    <!-- About Section -->
    <section class="section" id="about">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="section-header">
                <span class="section-tag"><i class="fas fa-user-shield"></i> About Me</span>
                <h2 class="section-title">Combining Security & Innovation</h2>
            </div>
            <div class="about-grid">
                <div class="about-text">
                    <!-- Photo -->
                    <img src="./ckjeurecom.jpg" alt="Charlyse Jobe" class="about-photo">
                    
                    <p class="about-intro">
                        I am a <strong>Cybersecurity Engineering student</strong> at EURECOM (Sophia Antipolis). It is a highly ranked, internationally focused engineering school. I am looking for a <strong>6-month internship starting in February 2027</strong>.
                    </p>
                    <p>
                        I attended intensive prep classes (MP2I/MPI) at Janson de Sailly. Then, I majored in cybersecurity at EURECOM. This path gave me strong skills in theoretical computer science and applied security.
                    </p>
                    <p>
                        My goal is to <strong>actively protect your systems and solve complex technical challenges</strong>.
                    </p>

                    <!-- International Mindset -->
                    <div class="why-korea" data-reveal>
                        <h3><span class="flag-icon">🌍</span> Global Mindset & Adaptability</h3>
                        <p>
                            I am currently on an exchange semester at Yonsei University in South Korea. This allows me to experience a top-tier tech ecosystem. I am used to international environments and speak several languages. I adapt quickly to new situations. I am ready to bring my open mind and technical skills to your team.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="about-card">
                    <div class="terminal-window">
                        <div class="terminal-header">
                            <span class="terminal-dot red"></span>
                            <span class="terminal-dot yellow"></span>
                            <span class="terminal-dot green"></span>
                            <span class="terminal-title">charlyse@portfolio:~</span>
                        </div>
                        <div class="terminal-body">
                            <p><span class="prompt">$</span> cat profile.json</p>
                            <pre><code>{
  "name": "Charlyse Jobe",
  "role": "Cybersecurity Engineer",
